cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper focuses on human action recognition and prediction using deep learning techniques, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The proposed method involves generating future frames, which can also be categorized under generative models (cs.AI). The experiments are conducted on video datasets, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the use of neural networks for feature extraction and prediction can also be categorized under neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
